{"tid":195573,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇羅斯仔又斷左ACL?","createTime":"2017-04-10T16:47:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-11T16:03:54.000Z","uid":92376,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9d85776b6b4bfc01a9f6c3b4d2d07e6d4493a6fa","tid":195573,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T16:47:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上星期先聽到佢戴帽,早兩日睇新聞話傷出,又斷左ACL,仲好似喊晒<br />\n係咪掛得靴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"549d74e74c83a90bbb5490e5ac4fb52ef10f4582","tid":195573,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T16:51:17.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=M80n4YL9TfmCcvG0giRsMrIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=e6729e53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】傷患這兩個字，是基奧斯比羅斯最大敵人；這位切爾達前鋒確定第3度十字韌帶受重傷，需要動手術並休戰7個月。<br />\n<br />\n今季由費倫天拿外借到切爾達的基奧斯比羅斯（Giuseppe Rossi）近日重拾狀態，上周在西甲對拉斯彭馬斯就個人大演帽子戲法。可惜，在周日聯賽主場鬥伊巴時，他正選上陣在35分鐘就因傷提早退下火線；球隊最終以0:2落敗。或者自知傷勢嚴重，羅斯在接受治理時流下男兒淚。<br />\n<br />\n周一，切爾達官方證實這位30歲意大利前鋒左膝前十字韌帶撕裂，需要接受手術，預計需要休戰7個月。<br />\n<br />\n羅斯職業生涯將再次因傷患受影響，特別是他和費倫天拿的合約，在今年6月就完結，續約機會不高。這名意大利前國腳的雙膝可說是多災多難，早年就試過右膝前十字韌帶撕裂，花了約兩年的時間，做了多次手術，才可以重返綠茵場。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : 互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e891d9ebc431190d53c9398e606b6384fc040e75","tid":195573,"uid":72621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T16:52:20.000Z","msg":"傷完一次之後隻腳會無咁好力<br />\n另一腳就好易受壓<br />\n所以好易傷埋"},{"pid":"14df7d3cde71bac8335bf32709e0daa24ab43a74","tid":195573,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T16:53:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>傷完一次之後隻腳會無咁好力<br />\n另一腳就好易受壓<br />\n所以好易傷埋</blockquote><br />\n即係你意思佢依家左右都傷過晒有平衡左,下次復出會好啲?"},{"pid":"ed24cc91f8c4d5f87a30562d1923ce8ef42ed028","tid":195573,"uid":72621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T16:54:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>傷完一次之後隻腳會無咁好力<br />\n另一腳就好易受壓<br />\n所以好易傷埋</blockquote><br />\n即係你意思佢依家左右都傷過晒有平衡左,下次復出會好啲?</blockquote><br />\n會兩隻腳都無力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a12c954b0dfb6e4305423cde30dfda2174e3fc8","tid":195573,"uid":7419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T16:55:39.000Z","msg":"以為講derrick rose"},{"pid":"28db5a43ca95e7d22430a198975445b973c48e44","tid":195573,"uid":65298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T16:56:29.000Z","msg":"以為 reus <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff802e0f4e02493cb1d6b9bba2f3a5edfb7d2045","tid":195573,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T16:58:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以為講derrick rose</blockquote><br />\n呢個唔係路斯咩,無聽過人叫佢羅斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3da15e203ef6ef857afad652f89783f0f2c66ec","tid":195573,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T16:58:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以為 reus <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a69005461953feb522407898399f67f7ffb9520","tid":195573,"uid":36324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T17:10:50.000Z","msg":"第幾多次 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e0f6c25dbd0eb32b36cd65bda4f41d8de2eb8aa","tid":195573,"u